{G : Type u_1} [inst : Group G] : Prop :=
∀ (H : Subgroup G), H < ⊤ → Subgroup.Normal H → IsCyclic H

def IsSaneGroup (G : Type u) [Group G] : Prop :=
  ∀ (N : Subgroup G), N < ⊤ → IsCyclic N
def IsSane (G : Type u) [Group G] : Prop := ∀ (N : Subgroup G), N.Normal → N ≠ ⊤ → IsCyclic N

def IsSaneGroup (G : Type u_1) [Group G] : Prop :=
  ∀ (H : Subgroup G), Subgroup.Normal H → H ≠ ⊤ → IsCyclic ↥H

{G : Type u_1} [inst : Group G] : Prop :=
  ∀ (N : Subgroup G), N.Normal → N ≠ ⊤ → IsCyclic N
{G : Type u_1} [inst : Group G] : Prop := ∀ (N : Subgroup G) [Subgroup.Normal N], N ≠ ⊤ → IsCyclic N

{G : Type u_1} [inst : Group G] : Prop :=
  ∀ (N : Subgroup G), N ≠ ⊤ ∧ Subgroup.Normal N → IsCyclic N
{G : Type u_1} [inst : Group G] : Prop := ∀ (N : Subgroup G), N.Normal → N ≠ ⊤ → IsCyclic N
{G : Type u_1} [inst : Group G] : Prop := ∀ (N : Subgroup G), N.Normal → N ≠ ⊤ → IsCyclic N

class SaneGroup (G : Type u_1) [Group G] :=
  (sane : ∀ (N : Subgroup G), N.Normal → N ≠ ⊤ → IsCyclic N)
